Drop TABLE if  exists public."analysis flights";
CREATE TABLE public."analysis flights"
(
	"estimated elapsed time" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	"total airtime" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode bytedict,
	"arrival delay" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode bytedict,
	"estimated arrival time" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	"cancellation code" VARCHAR(20) encode lzo,
	"cancelled flag" NUMERIC(2, 0) encode lzo,
	"scheduled arrival time" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	"scheduled departure time" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	"scheduled elasped time" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode bytedict,
	date TIMESTAMP encode lzo,
	"departure delay" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode bytedict,
	"estimated departure time" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	"flight distance" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	diverted VARCHAR(5) encode lzo,
	"flight code" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode delta32k,
	"late aircraft delay" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode lzo,
	"nas delay" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode lzo,
	"origin airport code" VARCHAR(20) encode bytedict,
	"destination airport code" VARCHAR(20) encode bytedict,
	"security delay" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode lzo,
	"tail number" VARCHAR(252) encode lzo,
	"carrier code" VARCHAR(251) encode lzo,
	"weather delay" NUMERIC(10, 0) encode lzo,
	"is departure delay" VARCHAR(5) encode bytedict,
	"is long delay" VARCHAR(5) encode lzo 
)
DISTSTYLE EVEN;

Drop TABLE if  exists public."analysis carriers";
CREATE TABLE public."analysis carriers"
(
	"carrier code" VARCHAR(50),
	"carrier name" VARCHAR(255)
)
DISTSTYLE ALL
SORTKEY
(
	"carrier code"
);

Drop TABLE if exists public."analysis airports";
CREATE TABLE public."analysis airports"
(
	"destination airport code" VARCHAR(255),
	"origin airport code" VARCHAR(255),
	"airport name" VARCHAR(255),
	city VARCHAR(255),
	state VARCHAR(255),
	country VARCHAR(255),
	latitude NUMERIC(12, 8),
	longitude NUMERIC(12, 8)
)
DISTSTYLE ALL
SORTKEY
(
	"origin airport code"
);


Drop TABLE if exists public."analysis planes";
CREATE TABLE public."analysis planes"
(
	"tail number" VARCHAR(50),
	manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
	"aircraft type" VARCHAR(255),
	model VARCHAR(255),
	"engine type" VARCHAR(255),
	"ownership type" VARCHAR(255),
	"issue date" VARCHAR(255),
	"manufacture year" NUMERIC(4, 0)
)
DISTSTYLE ALL
SORTKEY
(
	"tail number"
);

Drop TABLE if exists public."analysis weather";
CREATE TABLE public."analysis weather"
(
	"airport code" VARCHAR(5) encode lzo,
	date DATE encode delta,
	"average rainfall" NUMERIC(38, 2) encode bytedict
)
DISTSTYLE EVEN;

Drop TABLE if exists public."analysis carriers";
CREATE TABLE public."analysis carriers"
(
	"carrier code" VARCHAR(50),
	"carrier name" VARCHAR(255)
)
DISTSTYLE EVEN;
